---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import ServiceExplore from '../../components/ServiceExplore.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Teeth Whitening — Oasis Dental Care, Huntington Beach"
  description="Professional teeth whitening in Huntington Beach. In-office and take-home options with safe, lasting results from Dr. Jason Fu. Call (714) 893-2106."
  page="services"
>

<section class="phero">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumbs"><a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/services">Services</a><span class="sep">/</span><span style="color:#cfe6e2">Teeth Whitening</span></div>
    <span class="tag">Cosmetic dentistry</span>
    <h1>Teeth Whitening</h1>
    <p>Brighter teeth. Safer results. Professionally done.</p>
    <div class="acts">
      <a class="btn" href="/contact">Book a consultation <svg class="ico" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="tel:7148932106">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="split">
      <div>

        <div class="img-ph reveal">
          <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
          <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
          <span class="img-ph-desc">Bright, natural-looking smile — avoid overly artificial bleached look</span>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal">
          <span class="tag">Overview</span>
          <h2>A simple, effective way to refresh your smile.</h2>
          <p>Teeth whitening is one of the simplest ways to refresh your smile. Professional whitening removes stains more effectively and safely than over-the-counter products.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <h3>In-Office vs. Take-Home</h3>
          <p>We offer both options depending on your goals and timeline. In-office whitening delivers faster results in a single visit. Custom take-home trays allow gradual whitening on your schedule—with professional-grade gel for better results than store-bought kits.</p>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Patient in chair during whitening treatment, or take-home tray kit</span>
          </div>

          <h3>What Causes Staining?</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Coffee, tea, and wine</li>
            <li>Tobacco use</li>
            <li>Age-related yellowing</li>
            <li>Certain medications or foods</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>What to Expect</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Consultation to determine candidacy</li>
            <li>Shade assessment before and after</li>
            <li>Results that look natural, not artificial</li>
            <li>Guidance on maintenance to extend results</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="img-ph reveal">
            <div class="img-ph-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="3"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="9" r="1.5"/><path d="m21 15-5-5L5 21"/></svg></div>
            <span class="img-ph-lbl">Photo placeholder</span>
            <span class="img-ph-desc">Shade guide comparison, or before/after smile</span>
          </div>

          <h3>Is Whitening Right for You?</h3>
          <p>Whitening works best on natural tooth enamel. It won't change the color of crowns, veneers, or bonding. We'll assess your teeth and give you honest expectations before starting.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal" style="margin-top:48px">
          <span class="tag">Common questions</span>
          <h2 class="prose" style="margin-top:8px">Good to know.</h2>
          <div class="faq">
            <details open><summary>How long do whitening results last?</summary><p>With good habits—limiting staining foods and maintaining oral hygiene—professional whitening results typically last 1–2 years. Touch-up treatments can extend this further.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Will whitening cause sensitivity?</summary><p>Some patients experience mild, temporary sensitivity. We'll assess your teeth beforehand and recommend the best approach to minimize any discomfort.</p></details>
            <details><summary>Can whitening work on crowns or veneers?</summary><p>Whitening products only work on natural enamel. If your crowns or veneers no longer match after whitening, we can discuss replacement options.</p></details>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <aside>
        <div class="scard reveal">
          <div class="hd"><div class="grid-ov"></div><h3>Ask about whitening options</h3><p>In-office or take-home—your choice</p></div>
          <div class="bd">
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg><span>In-office treatment in about 1 hour</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg><span>Safe, professionally supervised results</span></div>
            <div class="row"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2 4 5v6c0 5 3.5 9 8 11 4.5-2 8-6 8-11V5l-8-3z"/></svg><span>ADA, CDC &amp; OSHA safety protocols</span></div>
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <a class="btn" href="/contact">Ask About Whitening Options</a>
            <a class="btn btn-out" href="tel:7148932106" style="justify-content:center">Call (714) 893-2106</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<ServiceExplore />

</Layout>
